<hymn_number>149</hymn_number>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1. Gitlohna lei hansedawl chungah,
 Thepna lei dogal henkawl buta;
 Suihlung mawla thihna lim nuoia lengte,
 Minthang Krista'n A thisan lun;
 In ei hung tandawk tai.

[V2]
 Aw , sietlei namtin vawnchawih,
 Thihna dailim nuoia ngabang lengte;
 Lal Krista nak liema thisan lul luong achun
 Hung kisilun na gitlohnau;
 Vuk bangin vam ina.

[V3]
 2. Hinna thisan luipi luong achun,
 Namtin, chitin din hinna a um;
 Kalvari tanga Lal Krista naka put,
 Kan tik neilo a kumsawtin;
 Nam tin thienna lui chu.

[V4]
 3. Gitloh vawm pen le a sawp thieng thei,
 Sietlei teu tui sawpthien guol loh chu;
 Kalvari hinna thisan lui luong achun,
 Hung kisil un, na gitlohnau;
 Vuk bangin vam ina.

[V5]
 4. Damna thisan lui a luon lai hin,
 Kin mengin, a nuoiah va buolin;
 Thihna thim dailim nuoia ngabang lengsa,
 Chang bang dam nan hehpihna thi-
 San lui ah va buolin.</lyrics>
<title>Krista Thisan a Kisil !</title>
</song>